  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3117330">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3117330/" class="title-link">经济学的指导意义</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3117330"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/anniedear/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u37374515-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/anniedear/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Annie</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-03-23"
      class="main-meta">2010-03-23 18:20:24</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3117330_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  如今经济学似乎也大热，从《牛奶可乐经济学》到《人人都爱经济学》。经济学的普及读物成了生活的另一种指导意义丛书。 不过此类读物也自有其的好处，王福重先生此书确是深入浅出，系统而经济，对于我等门外管窥者来说，一斑也具有一定的指导意义。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3117330/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3117330_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3117330_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



